# .gitignore — summary of changes and rationale
# Added by GitHub Copilot: summary + common ignores to keep the repository clean.
# Summary: ignore editor/project settings, virtual environments, build artifacts,
# and local credentials/temp files that should not be committed.
# Added: .vscode/, .idea/, node_modules/, *.env, .venv, venv/, __pycache__/,
# *.pyc, *.log, *.bak, *.tmp, *.swp, *.DS_Store, Thumbs.db, *.zip (local zips),
# local Office temp files (e.g. ~$*), and the existing secrets/ entry.
# Rationale: prevent accidental commits of credentials, editor-specific files,
# large binaries, and transient build artifacts.

# Credentials and API keys -- never commit
secrets/

# Editor/project settings
.vscode/
.idea/

# Node modules
node_modules/

# Python virtual environments and caches
.venv/
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Environment files and secrets
*.env

# Logs and temporary files
*.log
*.bak
*.tmp
*.swp

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Scratch space, if used
.scratch/

# Local/generated archives (ignore but note these were present earlier)
*.zip

